extendedInfo.description: The Only Place to Find Moving Companies. (usa only for now)We are in the process of adding more companies in your area, if there is a poor selection in your area, call smart move and we will find a good company near you for no charge!Here you will find only the best rated moving companies based on customer reviews, these companies have already been verified for licensing and insurance. Best of all, each company has provided a coupon that will significantly reduce the cost of your move just for using this application. Thank you for supporting the companies that care about you!
